{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}} {{Infobox newspaper | name = Negocio & Estilo de Vida | logo = | image = | caption = | type = [[Free newspaper|Free]] [[Business journalism|business newspaper]] | format = | owner = | founder = | publisher = Tumbo de privilegios, S.L. | editor = | chiefeditor = | assoceditor = | maneditor = | newseditor = | managingeditordesign = | campuseditor = | campuschief = | opeditor = | sportseditor = | photoeditor = | foundation = {{start date and age|2006|4|1|df=yes}} | political = | language = [[Spanish language|Spanish]] | ceased publication = | headquarters = | circulation = | sister newspapers = | ISSN = | oclc = | website = }}
'''''Negocio & Estilo de Vida''''' (simply ''Negocio'') is a [[Subscription|free subscription]] business daily newspaper published in [[Spain]].
==History and profile== ''Negocio'' was established in April 2006.<ref>{{cite web|title=Negocio & Estilo de Vida|url=http://www.miguelbuckenmeyer.com/work_proyecto.php?trabajo=1&proyecto=1|work=Buckenmeyer Co|accessdate=30 November 2014}}</ref><ref name=lau/> Its first issue was published on 23 May 2006.<ref name=nin>{{cite news|title=Spain: 5 business papers – 4 for free|url=http://www.newspaperinnovation.com/index.php/page/230/|accessdate=5 February 2015|work=Newspaper Innovation|date=23 March 2007}}</ref> The paper is the first free subscription business newspaper in Spain.<ref name=lau>{{cite web|author=Lauren Drablier|title=Spain: Free daily Negocio "blurs distinction" between free and paid content |url=http://www.editorsweblog.org/2008/09/23/spain-free-daily-negocio-blurs-distinction-between-free-and-paid-content|work=Newspaper Innovation|date=23 September 2008|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204162248/http://www.editorsweblog.org/2008/09/23/spain-free-daily-negocio-blurs-distinction-between-free-and-paid-content |archivedate=4 December 2014}}</ref> The publisher is Tumbo de privilegios, S.L., a subsidiary of Grupo Promecal.<ref name="publ">{{cite web|title=Spain: Top daily newspapers|url=http://www.publicitas.com/zh/home/media-news-events/news-detail/?newsid=44133&title=spain-top-daily-newspapers#.WOMxnBLygxc|work=Publicitas|accessdate=4 April 2017|date=13 December 2010}}</ref>
The circulation of ''Negocio'' in March 2007 was 68,000 copies.<ref name=nin/> In 2007 the paper had a circulation of 63,097 copies on weekdays.<ref>{{cite web|title=Spain: New circulation figures 2007 (newspapers)|url=http://www.adnative.net/en/global/media-news-events/news-detail/?newsid=22678&title=spain-new-circulation-figures-2007newspapers#.VHsyUGSsXRA|work=Adnative|accessdate=30 November 2014|date=13 May 2008}}</ref> In 2010 its circulation was 65,514 copies.<ref name="publ"/>
